rows.label: qev050603_MSG0001
rows.name:
Enough, human! ...Enough. We admit defeat.
The difference in our abilities is painfully clear.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050603_MSG0002
rows.name:
Now we must live not only with the shame of having
failed to defend our families, but of lacking the might
to avenge them ourselves.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050603_JNK0010
rows.name: Agree

rows.label: qev050603_SEL0011
rows.name: Tell the Wrothians that they lack strength.

rows.label: qev050603_JNK0020
rows.name: Disagree

rows.label: qev050603_SEL0021
rows.name: Praise the Wrothians for their strength.

rows.label: qev050603_MSG0003
rows.name:
I cannot argue with such a warrior.
There is no doubt much you could teach us.
But alas, the queen jacul was to be—[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050603_MSG0004
rows.name:
Yet it was not enough to best you. Rrrgh...
Still, the queen jacul is one foe we must—[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050603_MSG0005
rows.name:
Look, Brother! Are those not mortal jaculs,
minions to the queen herself?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050603_MSG0006
rows.name: What? Since when do they make territory here?![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050603_MSG0007
rows.name:
What do we do, my brother? My Skell is too damaged
from the last match to fight them.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050603_MSG0008
rows.name: ......[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050603_MSG0009
rows.name:
It seems I must ask you to show us your strength once
more, [ST:playername ].[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050603_MSG0010
rows.name:
Will you join us in slaying the vile beast and avenging
the family she brought low?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050603_JNK0030
rows.name: Accept

rows.label: qev050603_SEL0031
rows.name: Tell Da Naguth that he can count on you.

rows.label: qev050603_JNK0040
rows.name: Dismiss

rows.label: qev050603_SEL0041
rows.name: Coldly tell Da Naguth that you will do your job.

rows.label: qev050603_MSG0011
rows.name:
Thank you. I am eager for the chance to watch you
fight again.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050603_MSG0012
rows.name: Perhaps such cold pragmatism is what we lacked.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050603_MSG0013
rows.name:
I am eager for the chance to see you work, then.
Leave none alive.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050603_MSG0014
rows.name: Most impressive, [ST:playername ].[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050603_MSG0015
rows.name:
Let us return to the general.
Then we can formulate our plan for the hunt.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050603_MSG0016
rows.name:
It is a great honor to fight alongside one as strong as
yourself. I apologize for being a fool all this while.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050603_MSG0017
rows.name:
Speak for yourself! Unlike my brothers, human,
I am not so easily won over.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050603_MSG0018
rows.name:
I will not deny that you have great strength...
But it must be us who slay the demon![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050603_MSG0019
rows.name:
So know that it will be my hand which delivers the
killing blow, and do not stand in my way![ST:wait ]
